<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Arcade 8-Bit Web</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body, html {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
      background-color: #000;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .arcade-container {
      position: relative;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
      background: url('https://i.pinimg.com/736x/7b/91/a5/7b91a5eafeb1a90cefca3212df7f683a.jpg') no-repeat center center;
      background-size: contain;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .screen {
      position: absolute;
      width: 65%;
      height: 52%;
      background: rgba(10, 255, 10, 0.1);
      border: 3px solid #00ff00;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00ff00;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: #00ff00;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px #005500;
      backdrop-filter: brightness(1.3) contrast(1.2);
    }

    .content {
      min-height: 800px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border: 2px solid #00ff00;
      color: #00ff00;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: transparent;
      box-shadow: 3px 3px #005500;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #00ff00;
      color: #000;
      box-shadow: 1px 1px #002200;
    }

    @media(max-width: 768px) {
      .screen {
        width: 90%;
        height: 60%;
        font-size: 0.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="arcade-container">
    <div class="screen">
      <div class="content">
        <h1>â–¶ LET'S PLAY A GAME</h1>
        <p>Selamat datang di website retro 8-bit dalam mesin arcade!</p>
        <a href="https://link1.com" class="btn">â–¶ Link 1</a>
        <a href="https://link2.com" class="btn">â–¶ Link 2</a>

        <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">Ini konten yang bisa di-scroll ke bawah seperti biasa. Tambahkan apapun di sini!</p>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer in justo non metus.</p>
        <p>Donec pulvinar nec justo et placerat. ðŸŽ®</p>
        <p>Keep scrolling untuk melihat lebih banyak konten.</p>
        <p>...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

